comment: No one should be allowed to profit by using other people and destroying their lives.
commentable_entity.ask: Boycott #AmberTurd’s book when it comes out!
commentable_entity.title: Boycott #AmberTurd’s book when it comes out!
commentable_entity.description:
Clearly, Amber heard should not make one penny off a book about her lies, deceit and abuse for years against Johnny Depp! She has already stated that she will be writing a tell all book in the very near future, obviously because she needs money.  I feel that she should not be able to profit off of the misery she so “unthoughtfully” planned out forJohnny Depp! That would just be another slap in the face to the American justice system! If you agree with me please let’s gets this petition circulating now so that we can gather as many signatures as possible and get this out as public knowledge in hopes that nobody will buy this book! And I mean nobody!!! We all together have the power to stand as one and make it possible for this despicable person to not profit off of her lies deceit and cruelty!

 

Thank you!
